title: Creamy Raspberry Cheesecake Recipe
directions: COMBINE the biscuit crumbs and butter then press into the base of a greased and lined 20cm round springform pan. Chill.
BEAT the PHILLY and sugar with an electric mixer until smooth. Stir in the gelatine. Fold through the cream. Pour mixture over the prepared base. Refrigerate for 3 hours or until set.
DECORATE the cheesecake with strawberries before serving.
ingredients: 500g PHILADELPHIA Strawberry Block Cream Cheese, softened
3 teaspoons gelatine dissolved in ¼ cup boiling water
